OL,3,CFour more people arrested after man
OL,4,Cstabbed to death in city centre
OL,6,FFour more people have been arrested in
OL,7,Fconnection with the stabbing of a man
OL,8,Fin Leicester city centre.
OL,10,FTwo men, both aged 52, and two women,
OL,11,Fboth aged 43, are being questioned on
OL,12,Fsuspicion of assisting an offender.
OL,14,FIt comes after a man was stabbed on
OL,15,FWednesday night. The man in his 20s
OL,16,Fwas able to stop a police car on
OL,17,FLondon Road but died of his injuries
OL,18,Fon Thursday morning.
OL,20,FLeicestershire Police believe that he
OL,21,Fwas attacked in De Monfort Place.
