OL,3,CFour more people arrested after man
OL,4,Cstabbed to death in city centre
OL,6,FTen people in total have now been
OL,7,Farrested in connection with the attack.
OL,9,FSix men, aged between 18 and 33, were
OL,10,Farrested on suspicion of murder on
OL,11,FThursday, 23 July.
OL,13,FDetective Inspector Lorna Granville,
OL,14,Ffrom the East Midlands Special
OL,15,FOperations Unit Major Crime Team,
OL,16,Fsaid: "I'd like to thank people who
OL,17,Flive and work in the area for coming
OL,18,Fforward with information and assisting
OL,19,Fus, particularly in relation to
OL,20,Fcapturing vital CCTV.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/3
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,342,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F341A1784893683
OL,3,CFour more people arrested after man
OL,4,Cstabbed to death in city centre
OL,6,F"Although several people are in
OL,7,Fcustody, I'm continuing to appeal for
OL,8,Fanyone who has information but has not
OL,9,Fyet spoken to police to come forward.
OL,11,F"This includes anyone who was driving
OL,12,Fin the area between 10.30 pm and 11 pm
OL,13,Fon Wednesday night.
OL,15,F"Anything you can tell us, no matter
OL,16,Fhow insignificant you think it is,
OL,17,Fcould be important."
